bc7_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-313b3e98b8d1555dca1c7bf542272bc7_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e同学你好，我和你一样，是一名在读高中生。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e虽然我的数学成绩很差，也看不懂哥德巴赫猜想，但是我想跟你说，如果你真的想要为证明它而努力，那就不要在意别人的目光（虽然我知道忽略别人的眼光很难，但是你看，现在许多人都在等着看你的笑话，你必须保持冷静）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不论结局如何，我觉得你比那些只会冷言冷语的人要强多了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有些人还是积点口德比较好，真不明白冷嘲热讽一个想要证明哥德巴赫猜想的高中生对你们有什么好处？你证明哥猜为了什么学位什么奖，就不许他证明哥猜是为了上清北吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e期待打脸的人真不知道是什么心态。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560095242,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"4643b4e915a126151cb0220a060af8de","url_token":"gan-run-dong","name":"东临碣石","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/30703a6d42f6e4aa72fd66775d6041b2_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/30703a6d42f6e4aa72fd66775d6041b2_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/4643b4e915a126151cb0220a060af8de","user_type":"people","headline":"四色问题的民科终结者","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560095242","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545808715,"updated_time":1545808715,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e这里有一个四色定理的姊妹问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e本科生解决了四色定理人工证明是否可以拿菲尔兹奖。\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/306987629\" class=\"internal\"\u003e如果一个本科生人工证明了四色定理，能拿菲尔兹奖嘛。？\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e文体两开花，大家多多关注。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":564076870,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question"